description:
This is a 10 minute workout called '10 MIN DAILY STRETCH | Flexibility, Mobility and Relaxation | Daniela Suarez' from the channel Daniela Suarez.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This video is a 10 minute full body stretching routine that you can do dailyIt helps with flexibility, mobility and relazation! 

This video includes a sequence of different full body exercises, and it can be completed after your workouts, in the mornings or evenings! 

Don’t forget that stretching is extremely important to help your muscles recover!
